item.title: Cheer Chat with Jen Spell
item.description:
Season 2 of the hit docuseries, Cheer, has taken the world by storm. This week, Jenna brings on her friend and former cheerleader, Jen Spell, to break it all down. Tune in to hear Jen’s personal sports journey and her thoughts on the viral Netflix show.

item.title: Rooming in LA
item.description:
Jenna hopped off a plane at LAX (jk she flew into Burbank) and is here to chat with her roommates about their first week in LA. They discuss what they hope to achieve while being there and what makes their roommate dynamic work so well. (Hint: They are all just very weird.)

item.title: Off to LA
item.description:
In order to prep for her semester in Los Angeles, Jenna turns to Gerald, her friend and fellow Ithaca College student, who recently returned from his semester in LA. He shares his wildest stories, explains what it’s like being an LA transplant, and answers the question Jenna has been dying to know: Is Saddle Ranch really worth the hype?

item.title: A Kardashian Kristmas
item.description:

Jenna brings on her friend Sydney to discuss the glamorous Kardashians and admire the elaborate ways they celebrate Christmas. Bible, it’s a great episode.

item.description:

item.title: A Friendsgiving Special
item.description:

They catch up like good friends do and share what in pop culture they are must thankful for. To close things off they play a game of “Pass The Turkey”… you’ll have to tune in to hear what it’s all about.

item.title: Weird Celebrity Couples
item.description:
In Hollywood, you have the “it” couples, the divorcees, and the playboys, but what about those random celebrity couples? Maybe you forgot they dated, or maybe you never knew. This week, Jenna brings on her friend Tatum to delve into the weirdest, most random celebrity couples from the past. They then create some of their own random celebrity pairings, because why not??
